## 性能考虑 (Performance Considerations)

### Chinese Character Regex

Chinese characters use Unicode range `\u4E00-\u9FFF` (CJK Unified Ideographs)

**Performance impact:**
- ~10 additional regex patterns
- Minimal overhead (~5-10ms for 10KB document)
- Chinese character matching is efficient in modern JavaScript engines

### False Positive Handling

**Low false positive rate:**
- Gender: Only with context (性别:, 男性, 女性)
- Names: Only with labels (姓名:, 名字:) or titles (先生, 女士)
- Addresses: Only with address suffixes (省, 市, 区, 路, 号)
- Dates: Only with DOB labels (出生日期, 生日)

**Deliberate design choices:**
- Standalone names NOT detected (too many false positives)
- Random 男/女 characters NOT detected (only with context)
- Short address fragments NOT detected (minimum 5 characters)

